    "href": "about.html",
    "title": "About Me",
    "section": "",
    "text": "I am Yusuf Bora Çavdar, a 3rd-year Industrial Engineering student at Hacettepe University, expecting to graduate in 2026. My academic interests are centered around Data Science and Data Analytics. I am passionate about using data-driven insights to optimize processes and solve complex engineering problems.\nI am particularly interested in exploring the intersections of data analytics within Human Resources, focusing on Training and Development. Additionally, I have a strong interest in Lean and Six Sigma methodologies."
  },
